8. ML Prioritization Model

8.1 Model Overview
The CloudGuardian prioritization model uses machine learning to rank security findings by business impact, enabling teams to focus on the most critical issues first.

8.2 Feature Engineering
Feature	Description	Weight	Data Source
CVSS Score	Common Vulnerability Scoring System	30%	NVD Database
Exposure	Public vs Private access level	25%	CSPM Tool
Blast Radius	Potential impact scope	25%	Infrastructure Map
Compliance Impact	Regulatory violation severity	20%	Compliance Matrix

8.3 Priority Score Calculation
Priority Score = (CVSS × 0.30) + (Exposure × 0.25) + (Blast Radius × 0.25) + (Compliance × 0.20)

8.4 Priority Tiers
Score Range	      Priority	        Action Required
8.0 - 10.0	    🔴 CRITICAL	        Immediate remediation (hours)
6.0 - 7.9      	🟠 HIGH	          Prioritized remediation (days)
4.0 - 5.9	      🟡 MEDIUM	        Scheduled remediation (weeks)
0.0 - 3.9	      🟢 LOW	            Backlog consideration

